      "reason" : "BIGGEST_MUSIC_LISTENING_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let Glass Animals orbit your entire playlist",
      "description" : "You spun through the night and into morning with “A Tear in Space (Airlock)” looping across hours, Zedd and Bava’s “No Gravity” on repeat, and a steady parade of pop, dance, and indie. Glass Animals led the charge, but no single genre or mood held you back. 766 minutes, 235 tracks, 230 artists—your biggest music day of the year.",
