    }, {
      "columnQualifier" : "20251006",
      "minutesListened" : 0,
      "reason" : "MOST_ENERGETIC_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let “The Way I Are” set the tempo for a non-stop jump rope relay",
      "description" : "From sunrise to late night, “The Way I Are” by Timbaland, Keri Hilson, and D.O.E. kept returning like clockwork, anchoring a day built for movement. Between bursts of Glass Animals, Sabrina Carpenter, and Kid Rock, your queue was a high-voltage circuit of 30 energetic tracks. 319 minutes, 99 plays, 86 artists—your most energetic day of the year.",
