      "reason" : "MOST_NOSTALGIC_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you turned your queue into a pop time machine",
      "description" : "From morning’s “Bye Bye Bye” and “I Want It That Way” to afternoon disco with Bee Gees and Purple Disco Machine, your day jumped decades in a single playlist. Evening doubled down on nostalgia with “Stereo Hearts” and “Me And My Broken Heart” before looping “A Tear in Space (Airlock)” and “Espresso” into the night. 534 minutes, 178 tracks, 161 artists—your most nostalgic day of the year.",
      "filedUnderTags" : "[retro rewind, feel-good flashbacks]"
